9. Install smb-server
9.1 Install by apt-get
$ sudo apt-get install samba

9.2 Change /etc/samba/smb.conf file with help of smb.conf in github repo

9.3 Create share dir
$ sudo mkdir /var/smb

9.4. Allow read and write permissions
$ sudo chmod ugo+rwx /var/smb

9.5 Restart Samba

$ sudo service smbd restart
$ sudo service nmbd restart

9.6 Check and connect to samba-server. Type in Windows file explorer
//192.168.0.102

or for Linux
smb://192.168.0.102

where 192.168.0.102 - VM ip addres.

Check file permissions. Try to add folder, file. Delete folder.
